data.description: This charming 3-bedroom home with a study, is nestled in the tranquil neighborhood in Noble, at the end of a serene cul-de-sac. As you approach, you're greeted by a welcoming covered front porch, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or evening conversations with neighbors. Step inside through the dedicated entryway, and you'll be delighted by the airy open concept living space, flooded with natural light. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, ample cabinetry, and a huge pantry for all your culinary essentials. Gather around the cozy fireplace with gas logs in the living area, ideal for cozying up on chilly evenings. The wood look tile flooring throughout not only adds warmth but is also easy to maintain, ensuring convenience and style. Adjacent to the living area, you'll find a covered back porch, extending your living space outdoors and offering a peaceful retreat for dining or relaxation. This home features a dedicated utility room off the 2 plus car garage, complete with a built-in mud bench, keeping messes at bay and providing a convenient spot for storage and organization. The primary bedroom is generously sized and offers a large walk-in closet for all your wardrobe needs. The primary bathroom is a luxurious haven, featuring a tub, walk-in shower, and double vanity, providing the perfect retreat after a long day. Throughout the home, you'll find plenty of storage space, ensuring everything has its place and keeping clutter at bay. With its thoughtful design, convenient amenities, and peaceful location, this home offers comfortable and stylish living for you and your family.
